{"tid":1694843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過係催淚彈令周同學睇唔到路而墮樓？","createTime":"2019-11-05T10:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:25:21.000Z","uid":156582,"like":283,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"b9885f6771dd32731026ece17b4db8407c735487","tid":1694843,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"黑警從外向停車場室內射催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n周同學一方面好可能因受催淚氣體影響隻眼睇唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n二嚟催淚彈令停車場內煙霧彌漫大大降低視野<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅情況下周同學好大可能因此係逃生時走錯路線發生意外<br />\n<br />\n黑警一直事無忌旦咁亂放催淚彈，用驅散為由係冇評估過現場環境就放，一直未出事大家就覺得冇野，而家終於造成不可挽回嘅慘劇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢兩點好合理地推論到黑警直接導致今次悲劇發生<br />\n大家千祈唔好Miss左呢點<br />\n<br />\n再加埋阻礙急救令傷者延醫，周同學有咩事嘅話黑警就百份百係殺人兇手！"},{"pid":"395f92131df991ec6a345b7ea6051afe578f33bb","tid":1694843,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45317a73cbd0ca972a943f04ff314e065964533b","tid":1694843,"uid":156582,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"核彈呀！推爆佢啦！"},{"pid":"e7933fa35f6c356a58e006db8572d305deb519d3","tid":1694843,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eacad729629e2e8e796188dcc4956d36b3820f","tid":1694843,"uid":273991,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:11:33.000Z","msg":"就算冇肉眼睇到既煙霧<br />\n食緊彈對眼都&quot;拿&quot;到打唔開, 狂標淚水<br />\n真係會睇唔到路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係最好有CCTV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16f13dd155979b3d57a4943590cda9fc905a414","tid":1694843,"uid":156582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95eacad729629e2e8e796188dcc4956d36b3820f","tid":1694843,"uid":273991,"like":43,"dis